longBusinessSummary: Delticom AG, together with its subsidiaries, operates as an online distributor of tires and automotive accessories in Germany and Europe. Its focuses on selling tyres and wheels online. The company sells its tires to retail and commercial customers for passenger cars, motorbikes, trucks, utility vehicles, buses, and wheel sets. The company operates 440 online shops and online distribution platforms in 75 countries. Delticom AG was founded in 1999 and is based in Hanover, Germany.
